viewData.name: Luxury 3D Eyelashes 10
viewData.short_description: The PhiNesse eyelashes are natural and handmade. Each eyelash is made to look as natural as possible.
viewData.long_description: The PhiNesse eyelashes are natural and handmade. Each eyelash is made to look as natural as possible. The eyelashes are soft, flexible, easy to apply and comfortable to wear. The luxury 3D eyelashes are designed to give a dramatic look. They are thick but also long, so they add volume and length - those hit two priorities at a time.
